@startuml
title [RF010] - Editar/Excluir Animais

actor ONG as "Admin ONG"
participant UI as "Interface UI"
participant Backend as "Back End"
database DB as "Banco de Dados"

ONG ->> UI: Seleciona animal
UI ->> Backend: PUT/DELETE /api/animais/{id}
Backend ->> DB: UPDATE/DELETE animais
DB -->> Backend: Sucesso
Backend -->> UI: Operação concluída
UI -->> ONG: Confirmação
@enduml
